# v16 Session 3 fix — filesystem-walker integration-test fixtures
# live under crates/strata-fs/tests/fixtures/ and are committed
# intentionally as one-time snapshots (HFS+ via Session D, FAT16
# via Session E, APFS via Session 1.5 probe fixture moved in
# Session 3). Sessions D/E session state claimed "committed" but
# the *.img pattern above was silently blocking them — this
# un-ignore restores the intent.
!crates/strata-fs/tests/fixtures/*.img

